skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ocean waves
des: Let the blissful sounds of the oceans waves lull you right to sleep! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Ocean Waves,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
